Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# GMAIL ACCOUNT

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User tomvig38@gmail.com
Port 993
PassCmd "+/usr/local/bin/lpass show -p Mutt"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Messages envoy&AOk-s"
Slave :gmail-local:sent

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Corbeille"
Slave :gmail-local:trash

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-trash

